1. Write a program to sort the elements in odd positions in descending
order and even  elements in ascending order

Eg 1: Input: 13,2 4,15,12,10,5

13,4,12,5

4,5,12,13//even position
i%2==0 and j%2==0
then sorting for ascending oder

2,15,10//odd position
i%2==1 and j%2==1
then sorting for decending order



Output: 13,2,12,10,5,15,4

Eg 2: Input: 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9
Output: 9,2,7,4,5,6,3,8,1
